<div style="margin-bottom:20px;">
  <div style="font-size:15px; font-weight:800; color:#2E2E38; margin-bottom:6px;">Kòd Konekte Ou</div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#5D6345;">Antre kòd sa a nan paj konektesyon Zèllus pou kontinye.</div>
</div>

<div style="background:#2E2E38; border:2px solid #C5A059; border-radius:14px; padding:24px; margin-bottom:16px; text-align:center;">
  <div style="color:#C5A059; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2px; margin-bottom:10px;">Kòd 6 Chif</div>
  <div style="color:#fff; font-size:34px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:10px; font-family:'Courier New', monospace;">
    <%= @code %>
  </div>
  <div style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size:11px; margin-top:12px;">
    Li ekspire nan <%= @ttl_minutes %> minit
  </div>
</div>

<div style="background:#fff; border:1px solid #d9d6c4; border-radius:12px; padding:14px; margin-bottom:16px;">
  <div style="color:#2E2E38; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:4px;">
    🔒 Pou sekirite ou
  </div>
  <div style="color:#5D6345; font-size:11px; line-height:1.5;">
    Pèsonn nan Zèllus pa p janm mande w kòd sa a. Si w pa t mande kòd sa a, ou ka inyore imèl la — kont ou rete an sekirite.
  </div>
</div>
